{
  "stem": "21437.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is when that it hit me when they put me to the place that I still stayed there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put on me the number on a piece of string, engraved on a piece of metal, and the number was 26748.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when this happened-- and that was they not they put it not only by force, but it was-- there were all kinds of shapes of heads.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were only one size of this string.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even that bit of string was too much to give us as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was really you can barely push it through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And now it was here, it was right here-- and I had a thin neck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it had to be visible at all-- it had to be visible at all times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I thought something happened to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I thought surely there is more-- if I'm alive, there must be more to it than just my physical body.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I refuse to live-- I talk to myself, I am not just this physical body.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Surely I know that I've got a soul and a spirit as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'm not going just to go like this, just to think that if I get that bit of bread, or if I get that bit of water, you know, if I this, that I can't, you know?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All those thoughts that you had because all that you could focus, it was the work and then it was if you're going to get that bit of bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to get it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not going to get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then you looked if others need you bit of bread to save them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things like this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So nothing else really, you know, mattered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I told, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
